      <body>
         <div>
            <head>21.4.1882 Freitag</head>
            <p>
               <placeName type="write" key="49096">Paris</placeName> April 21. 1882.
                  Friday</p>
            <p> Drove out with Baby<note type="reg">
                  <persName key="104">Brion, Wilma</persName>
               </note> in the afternoon.
               In the evening <persName key="176">Papa</persName> and I went to <orgName key="70144">the Opera</orgName> where we saw the new opera of <persName key="1128">A.
                  Thomas</persName> &#x201e;<name type="work" key="28430">Françoise de Rimini</name>.&#x201c; It
               was only the fourth <add hand="hgk">night</add>. The story is taken out of <persName key="6680">Dante&#x2019;s</persName> &#x201e;Inferno&#x201c;<note type="reg">
                  <name type="work" key="28563">La Divina Commedia</name>
               </note>. There are some very fine decors especially two representing different parts
               of the &#x201e;Inferno&#x201c;. But the music does by no means come up to them.
            </p>
         </div>
